    <h1>Maine Coon Cat Care Guide</h1>
    <p><strong>Breed:</strong> Maine Coon Cat</p>
    <p><strong>Age:</strong> 12-15 years (average lifespan)</p>
    <p><strong>Size:</strong> Large</p>
    
    <h3>General Care Tips:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Exercise: Maine Coons are playful and active, so they require plenty of interactive playtime.</li>
        <li>Diet: Their large size means they need a higher-calorie, high-protein diet.</li>
        <li>Grooming: Their long coats require regular grooming (2-3 times per week) to prevent tangles.</li>
        <li>Health: Regular vet visits to check for heart disease, hip dysplasia, and dental care.</li>
    </ul>
    
